message:
Fix a longstanding NPE.

Do not access objects in onCreate() of fragments, as the parent activity will not have been initialized
at that point when it is being recreated by system (e.g. on devide rotation). Safe to access in
 onActivityCreated() as onCreate() would have been called at that point.
